citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:38-2:08pm on 07-
SEP-2023.
The inspector knocked on the facility door multiple times as well as called and messaged the phone number on the
account. The inspector left the facility after 30 minutes of waiting with no contact. The licensee then called the inspector to
say that no one was available to do the inspection.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:38-2:08pm on 07-
SEP-2023. 
 
The inspector knocked on the facility door multiple times as well as called and messaged the phone number on the 
account. The inspector left the facility after 30 minutes of waiting with no contact. The licensee then called the inspector to 
say that no one was available to do the inspection. 
 
 
End Section
